spec_data.Name: PragmARC-devel
spec_data.Description:
The PragmAda Reusable Components (PragmARCs) is a library of containers,
algorithms and utility components for Ada, ranging from the basic-but-essential
to the high-level.

The PragmARC-devel package contains source code and linking information for
developing applications that use PragmARC.
